      IsoId=Q8LBP4-1; Sequence=Displayed;
    Name=2;
      IsoId=Q8LBP4-2; Sequence=VSP_011358, VSP_011359;
      Note=Derived from EST data. No experimental confirmation
      available;
-!- TISSUE SPECIFICITY: Mainly expressed in organs that contain green
    tissues such as leaves, flower buds and stems.
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the OXA1/oxaA family.
